Thumbnail Concept
Video Title: I Asked ChatGPT to Run My Day – Here’s What Happened
Thumbnail Text (3–4 words):
 AI Controlled My Day
Primary Emotion:
 Surprise / Curiosity
Visual Layout:
Split-screen composition


Left side: messy desk, stressed or tired expression, phone notifications


Right side: clean desk, calm expression, organized schedule or checklist


Design Elements:
ChatGPT icon or chat bubble pointing toward the organized side


Bold arrow highlighting transformation


Minimal but expressive facial focus


Color Scheme:
Bright background (yellow or light blue)


High contrast between text and background


White text with dark outline for mobile visibility


Font Style:
Bold sans-serif (Anton, Bebas Neue, or similar)


AI Image Generation Prompt:
YouTube thumbnail image with a split-screen layout.
Left side shows a stressed person at a messy desk with phone notifications.
Right side shows the same person calm at a clean desk with an organized schedule.
Bright colors, high contrast, modern YouTube style, expressive emotions


